===Influence===
Speaking in an interview with ''Frontier Psychiatrist'', [[Iain McGilchrist]], author of ''[[The Master and His Emissary]]'', a book about the world views of the two hemispheres of the brain, stated: "What I began to see – and it was John Cutting's work on the right hemisphere that set me thinking – was that the difference lay not in what they do, but how they do it."<ref name="FrontierPsychiatrist"/>

